---
import Layout from "../layout/index.astro"
---
<Layout>
    <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center pt-12 flex-col">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-semibold text-vatscaSnow ">Copenhagen Live 2024</h1>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-6 ml-12 mr-12 mt-12 gap-12">
            <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-4 shadow">
                <div class="h-12 bg-[#1a475f] text-vatscaSnow flex items-center pl-6">
                    About
                </div>
                <div class="h-fit bg-vatscaSnow text-vatscasecondary p-4">
                    <h1>👋 Hello controllers</h1>
                    <p class="text-sm">
                        The time has come for the 8th annual Copenhagen LIVE, on September 21th in Copenhagen.<br/>
                        This year will be diffrent as we have a new location! We will be hosting live in the same building as where X-Faktor is produced! and if that dose not excite you, there will be air condition!
                    </p>
                    <br/>
                    <p class="text-lg font-semibold pt-4">NOTAM</p>
                    <ul class="text-sm">
                        <li>
                            🚗 Parking is included and available at the location.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            🖥️ Bring your own computer and setup. Cabled ethernet and wireless internet will be avilable.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            🛌 We are currently working on a discount for the hotel next door, TBD.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            📍 Priorparken 230, 2605 Brøndby, Danmark
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            🗓️ 20-21-22 September 2024
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            💶 250 DKK
                        </li>
                    </ul>
        
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-2 shadow bg-white">
                <div class="h-12 bg-[#1a475f] text-vatscaSnow flex items-center pl-6 min-w-72">
                    Attendee Pricing
                </div>
                <div class="h-64 bg-vatscaSnow text-vatscasecondary p-4">
                    <p>💶 250 DKK Upfront</p>
                    <hr class="border-2 mt-2 mb-2 border-[#1a475f]"/>
                    <p class="text-sm pt-6">Last year, the self-payment has amounted to about 250 DKK (25-35 euro) for the whole weekend. We are anticipating the same this year, but may vary. Price is adjusted compared to what you are participating in.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-4">
                <div class="h-12 bg-[#1a475f] text-vatscaSnow flex items-center pl-6">
                    Agenda
                </div>
                <div class="h-fit bg-vatscaSnow text-vatscasecondary p-4">
                    <h2 class="font-semibold">General timeline, more information to be posted</h2>
                    <hr />
                    <br />
                    <p>Firday is preperation and setup days, all controlers are encuraged to come and setup their station as soon as possible to start enjoying eachother company</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>Saturday is event day, starting at 6z with brekfirst (egg & bacon) and then following the roster for each position. Event ends at 22z</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>Sunday is cleanup day, please be avilable if you dont need to be anywhere else as this makes it only take one hour enstad of 5.</p>
                    <br />
                    <p> </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-2 shadow h-fit">
                <div class="h-12 bg-[#1a475f] text-vatscaSnow flex items-center pl-6 min-w-72">
                    Attendee Documents
                </div>
                <div class="h-fit bg-vatscaSnow text-vatscasecondary p-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
                    <a href="files/cphlive-regulations-2024.pdf" class="p-2 bg-[#1a475f] text-vatscaSnow rounded-sm text-white">CPH Live Redulations</a>
                    <a href="files/cphlive-photo-video-2024.pdf" class="p-2 bg-[#1a475f]  text-vatscaSnow rounded-sm text-white">Picture & Video Consent declaration</a>
                    <a href="files/cphlive-gcp-2024.pdf" class="p-2 bg-[#1a475f]  text-vatscaSnow rounded-sm text-white">Guardian Consent Form</a>
        
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-2 shadow h-fit">
            </div>
          </div>
    </div>
</Layout>